    "description": "成为森林大火，烧毁眼前的一切！每个像素都是物理模拟的。烧毁树木、建筑物、车辆和尖叫的小人类。躲避子弹地狱雨云和生气的消防员以活下去。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242220/extras/1b39a76521438798b8ab2a922d01ad6e.poster.avif?t=1726370944\" width=622 height=382 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242220/extras/1b39a76521438798b8ab2a922d01ad6e.webm?t=1726370944\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242220/extras/1b39a76521438798b8ab2a922d01ad6e.mp4?t=1726370944\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>不要以为你会毫无抵抗地燃烧。大自然母亲派出了一排子弹般的雨云和其他障碍物来结束你的毁灭盛宴。你的火焰必须穿过风暴才能生存。消防直升机，飞机和小消防员也会出来接你。你烧他们的建筑越多，他们就越生气（你得到的组合点就越多！）<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242220/extras/aa71ffc08d4224383c94700f959f9a36.poster.avif?t=1726370944\" width=800 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242220/extras/aa71ffc08d4224383c94700f959f9a36.webm?t=1726370944\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242220/extras/aa71ffc08d4224383c94700f959f9a36.mp4?t=1726370944\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>这是一个流氓精简版游戏，所以每次运行都是不同的。但是，我们仍然保持着持续升级点的进步感。这意味着你会变得更强壮，即使你死了5000次。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242220/extras/1fc7f6593784e8a846ed98077ca9f090.poster.avif?t=1726370944\" width=540 height=540 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242220/extras/1fc7f6593784e8a846ed98077ca9f090.webm?t=1726370944\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242220/extras/1fc7f6593784e8a846ed98077ca9f090.mp4?t=1726370944\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>森林火灾不仅限于树木...点燃整个人群，从天空中引爆直升机，并烧毁著名的纪念碑。你的毁灭没有边界，不受道德的阻碍。<br><br>森林是广阔而无止境的，她内心隐藏着无数的秘密。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特征</h2>- 5个独特的关卡<br>- 3种游戏模式：主线任务，无尽模式和疯狂模式<br>- 流氓精简版风格永久死亡<br>- 数十种痛苦的子弹地狱图案<br>- 可解锁和持久升级系统<br>- 30+成就和持久的统计数据<br>- 数十个秘密;人物、纪念碑和怪物<br><br>...而这一切都比午餐的价格还便宜！你准备好燃烧了吗？",
